\begin_inset Flex CharStyle:Pkg
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
RUnit
\end_layout

\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Flex CharStyle:Pkg
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
svUnit
\end_layout

\end_inset

 is interchangeable).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Finally, 
\begin_inset Flex CharStyle:Pkg
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
svUnit
\end_layout

\end_inset

 is also designed to be integrated in the 
\begin_inset Flex SciViews
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

\end_layout

\end_inset

 GUI (
\begin_inset Flex URL
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

http://www.sciviews.org/SciViews-K
\end_layout

\end_inset

), on top of Komodo Edit or IDE (
\begin_inset Flex URL
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

http://www.activestate.com/komodo_edit
\end_layout

\end_inset

), and to approach extreme programming practices with automatic code testing
