 A rather simple interface is provided to link and pilot 
\begin_inset Flex CharStyle:Pkg
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
svUnit
\end_layout

\end_inset

 from any GUI/IDE, and the Komodo Edit/IDE implementation could be used
